Localisation-cUserLocalisedString.English: Good afternoon, driver. Please depart when ready and head for St Blazey. It should be a pretty simple run with no booked stops, when we arrive at St Blazey there will be a small amount of shunting to carry out before we end our trip.
We may be held for 2B53 as it arrives at Par (Booked 13:35). We will then need to head round the curve and past St Blazey box to reverse into the yard itself.
We have the token, head out onto the signal track until the rear of the train clears the next signal.
Now set back onto St Blazey Fowey Main.
Uncouple from the train and move forward until you clear the points to access the Fuel Line
Good work this afternoon, a decent test run for 37053!
